properties.Name: RelatedLegalEntity
properties.Description:
A legal entity related to the associated legal entity.

Note:
This may also be defined by the DUN's relationship/hierarchy.

Columns.Name: LegalEntityId
Columns.Description:
The unique identifier of a Legal Entity.

In this case it is the business, organization or legal entity whose books are being recorded and financial statements presented.

Columns.Name: RelatedLegalEntityId
Columns.Description:
The unique identifier of a related Legal Entity.

In this case it is the business, organization or legal entity who books are being recorded and financial statements presented.

Columns.Name: PeriodStartDate
Columns.Description: The period start date of the legal entity relationship.

Columns.Name: PeriodEndDate
Columns.Description: The period end date of the legal entity relationship.

Columns.Name: LegalEntityRelationshipTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of the Legal Entity Relationship Type.

Columns.Name: LegalEntityRelationshipNote
Columns.Description: A note, comment or additional information regarding the related legal entities.
